name: Silver Bamboo Earrings
description:
Silver Bamboo Earrings are long delicate earrings inspired by the bamboo plant. They are made with sterling silver wire and glass resins. 
The bamboo has leaves of deep emerald color that changes its shade depending on the light. It can look quite dark but when the leaves catch the lights they become bright and shiny.

The bamboo stems measure approx 6cm.

materials: sterling silver wire; glass resins;

name: Sky Full Of Stars Silver Earrings
description:
Sky Full Of Stars Earrings are circle earrings made with sterling silver wire and transparent glass resins. 
The picture in each earring is of a beautiful night landscape with trees, dark blue sky full of stars and a moon.

The effect of the piece changes with the change of light - in indirect light the earrings look like dark ultramarine circles while on the passing light the colors become more vivid and the whole picture becomes alive.
Circles measure about 1.5cm.


materials: sterling silver wire; glass resins;

name: Red Landscapes Earrings. Copper Earrings.
White Flowers Earrings
description:
White Flowers are earrings made with clay, varnishes and sterling silver wire.
Two gentle white flowers are hanging on a sterling silver stems, the inside of the blossoms is of a vivid yellow color.
The earrings are very tender and light.

The earrings measure 5cm top to bottom (including the ear wires).

materials: papier-mache clay; varnishes; sterling silver;

name: Oxidized Triangles Silver Earrings
description:
Oxidized Triangles Silver Earrings are made with sterling silver wire. 
In a triangle frame made with thick silver wire I created a beautiful pattern with fine silver wire. Then I oxidized the whole piece and gently polished it to bring back some of its shine.
The Triangle Earrings look very elegant and classy.

The earrings measure about 5cm top to bottom (2inches).

materials: sterling silver wire

name: Faces Earrings
description:
Faces earrings are unique earrings made with dark copper wire.
For each piece I created a character, the pairs consist of a couple of two faces each with its own features.
The colors are bright and shiny on passing light but otherwise the earrings look darker.

The ovals measure about 3cm top to bottom.

Please when making a purchase leave a note about which is the couple of your choice.
They can be best seen on the 3rd picture:
1.Blue
2.So many things to tell
3.So glad to see you again

Thank you!

materials: copper wire; glass resins;

name: Green Leaves Earrings
description:
Green Leaves Earrings are long elegant earrings made with sterling silver wire and emerald green glass resin. 
The fine wire creates beautiful patterns in the leaf which then are enhanced by the green color.

The earrings measure approx 6cm.

materials: sterling silver; emerald green glass resin;

name: Silver Dragonfly Brooch
description:
Silver Dragonfly Brooch is made with various thickness sterling silver and fine silver wire. 
With thick sterling silver wire I first made the dragonfly frame in which with fine silver wire I created a beautiful pattern.

The brooch measures about 6.5cm across (2.5inches).
The dragonfly is made of silver wire but please notice that the pin only is metal (nickel-free).

materials: fine silver; sterling silver; metal;

name: Close Up Dragonfly Earrings
description:
Close Up Dragonfly Earrings are summer inspired earrings made with sterling silver wire and glass resins. The earrings are of a hoop type and there is a picture in each hoop. One is a landscape with a dragonfly flying over still water and leaves of grass, while the other shows the dragonfly wing in detail. There is a touch of a sunshine in the landscape too. 
The earrings were gently oxidized and polished to enhance the detail.

Hoops measure approx 3cm top to bottom.

materials: sterling silver wire; glass resins;

name: Black Cat Earrings
description:
Black Cat Earrings are silver hoops made with sterling silver wire. 
There is a cat sitting in the hoop, each cat is different.
From some angles the earrings look like simple hoops while from others the cats are catching the attention. The effect can be seen on the last picture.

The earrings measure a bit over 3cm top to bottom.

materials: sterling silver; black enamel;

name: Close Up Dragonfly Necklace
description:
Close Up Dragonfly Necklace is a dragonfly inspired sterling silver necklace.
Using silver wire I made a dragonfly wing which after that I colored in light blue gradating to transparent.
The dragonfly wing hangs on a gently oxidized ball chain.
The necklace is asymmetrical with the wing positioned right to the center.

Length of the necklace: 43cm
Dragonfly wing: approx. 4cm
Made to order!
Please allow ten days for the necklace to be made and send.

materials:
sterling silver; glass resins;

name: Blue Dragonfly Earrings
description:
Blue Dragonfly Earrings are dragonfly inspired copper earrings. 
In a copper oval I created a picture for each earring - a picture of a summer landscape with leaves of green grass and sunshine. There is a dragonfly flying over the grass in only one of the earrings.

Ovals measure about 3cm.
The ear wires are copper too.

materials: copper wire; glass resins;

name: Black Cat White Cat earrings
description:
Black Cat White Cat earrings are sterling silver hoop earrings. 
There is a cat sitting in each hoop - in one of the earrings it's a white cat and in the other - a black one.

In some angles the earrings look like simple hoops - the effect can be seen on the second picture.

Hoops measure approx 3 cm top to bottom.

materials: sterling silver wire; white&black enamel;

name: Dragonfly Earrings. Copper round earrings.
description:
Copper Dragonfly Earrings are round colorful earrings. 
Inspired by the summer, they show a picture of a green field in a sunny day - the sun is shining and in one of the earrings there is a purple dragonfly flying around.

The circles measure 3cm.
The earrings you'll receive will be of the same design and made with the same care, but please have in mind that since my work is completely hand made every pair is unique and slightly different.

materials: copper wire; glass resins

name: Waves Blue Silver Earrings
description:
Waves Blue Earrings are silver hooks made with sterling silver wire and transparent blue resin. Each earring is a rough blue sea.

In indirect light the colors look darker while on passing light they are bright and shiny.
Hoops measure approx 3cm top to bottom.


materials: sterling silver wire; glass resins;

name: Red Necklace. 14K Gold Filled Necklace.
description:
Red Necklace is a delicate necklace made with 14K gold filled wire, gold filled chain and transparent glass resin.
Inspired by nature, the wire forms lines and circles reminding a branch with gentle leaves. The color is deep red.

The piece is 40cm long, small adjustments in the length can be made.

materials: 14K gold filled wire and chain; red glass resin;

name: Sunflower Earrings. Round copper earrings.
description:
Sunflower earrings are round earrings made with dark copper wire and colored in my special glass resin technique. 
The colors look vivid and bright in direct light, otherwise the earrings are more subtle.

The circles measure 3cm.

materials: copper wire; glass resins;

name: Red Poppies Earrings
description:
Red Poppies Earrings are sterling silver earrings made with wire and transparent glass resin.
In a small rectangular frame with wire I created a picture with red poppies and a touch of a sunshine which after that I colored in my special glass resin technique. The colors are bright and beautiful and change their intensity and shade with the light.

The frames measure about 1cm-1.5cm and hang on beautiful 3cm long ear wires.

Each pair is unique but made with the same care and attention.

materials: sterling silver wire; glass resins;
